{"type": "article", "id": 7100, "title": "Mercure Lamp 自动开关灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-05T07:28:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234346oOBgudbXcJlRi0et.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">法国设计师 Lucie Le Guen 的这件作品叫做 Mercure Lamp，是一款可以依靠本身的倾斜程度自动开关的灯。灯的外表成菱形，内部放置了小钢珠。这些小钢珠的作用就是开关灯，当灯向一侧倾斜，小钢珠聚集在下部，会触发开关，反之，当小钢珠聚集在另一端，灯会自动关上。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052343443e5noAQM4hkxl9r2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234344MpRYIBU3CkgTSflV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052343451JuTfXn3Bw0xoceY.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234345gDQCHOvwViZE392a.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n<br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}